      "content": "but you're just adding emotional weight to something that doesn't have it. if the outcome is the same, why is one option \"better\" than the other? if I decide that the absence of pain is more efficient than the struggle to find \"moments of joy,\" isn't that just a more logical way to handle the equation?",
